               <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard ">Risk of electromagnetic disturbance</typeofhazard>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">This is a product Category C3 according to IEC 62040-2.
This is a product for commercial and industrial applications in the
second environment - installation restrictions or additional measures
may be needed to prevent disturbances. The second environment includes
all commercial, light industry, and industrial locations other than
residential, commercial, and light industrial premises directly connected
without intermediate transformer to a public low-voltage mains supply.
The installation and cabling must follow the electromagnetic compatibility
rules, e.g.:<sl class="- topic/sl ">
                     <sli class="- topic/sli ">the segregation of cables,</sli>
                     <sli class="- topic/sli ">the use of shielded or special cables when relevant,</sli>
                     <sli class="- topic/sli ">the use of grounded metallic cable tray and supports.</sli>
                  </sl>
               </howtoavoid>
